Hello World Souffle.

Ingredients.
72 g haricot beans
101 eggs
108 g lard
108 g lard
111 g lard

Method.
Put haricot beans into the mixing bowl.
Put eggs into the mixing bowl.
Put lard into the mixing bowl.
Put lard into the mixing bowl.
Put lard into the mixing bowl.
Liquefy contents of the mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
